description:
Email address verification technology that connects to mailboxes and checks whether an email address exists.

Then it tells you whether the email address is real or not. It extracts the MX records from the email address and connect to mail server (over SMTP and also simulates sending a message) to make sure the mailbox really exist for that user/address. Some mail servers do not co-operate in the process, in such cases, the result of this email verification tool may not be as accurate as expected.
